        <h2>
            胡适书信集(上中下)的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5359869">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5359869/" class="title-link">很值得读的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5359869"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/57729463/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u57729463-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57729463/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">泠弦堂</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-25"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-25 10:30:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5359869_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  胡适先生的传记很多，但缺少佳作。其中最有意义的《胡适先生年谱长编初稿》此书是台北联经出版公司出的，共有十大本。我翻遍网上当当网、卓越网、蔚蓝网三大网上书店的“巨无霸”，此书也是不见踪影。又卷帙浩繁通读不易，但这本《胡适书信集》则是一本了解胡适先生生平与思想...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5359869/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5359869_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5359869_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
